calibration_step.instruction: it's just a jump to the left
16 ch calibration - click "next"
EMG Right Leg calibration. Click "Next" to continue
Flex-point your right foot 3 times with 5 seconds breaks
Calibration  - EMG Left Leg. Click "Next" to continue
Flex-point your left foot 3 times with 5 seconds breaks
Sit in upright position for 10 seconds
Calibration - ECG. Click "Next" to continue
Chew for 5 seconds
Swallow 3 times with 5 seconds breaks in between
Move your eyes up and down slowly for 5 times. wait about one second in between movements
Move your eyes sideways slowly for 5 times. wait about one second in between movements
Blink slowly with 1 second in between blinks for 20 seconds
Keep you eyes open and try not to move them for 2 minutes
Close your eyes for 2 minutes
Calibration - face. Click "Next" to continue
Calibration - ECG. Click "Next" to continue
Sit in upright position for 10 seconds
Calibration - EMG Left Leg
Flex-point your left foot 3 times with 5 seconds breaks
Flex-point your right foot 3 times with 5 seconds breaks
Hold your breath for 10 seconds
Breathe normally for 10 seconds
Calibration-Respiratory
